originalText.text: After suffering an accident nearly two years ago and living in chronic pain 44th Street Health & Wellness has me back on track to a pain free life. The combination of different therapies used is no doubt the reason I am now able to sleep through the night again and have regained much of my range of motion and flexibility. After having spent months in Physical Therapy at a different office with little to no improvement in just a few short weeks the team at 44th Street Health and Wellness had developed my path to recovery. The staff and therapists are top notch. You don't have to live with chronic pain if your treatment plan is well prepared and executed. This is the place to go if you want to get better.

originalText.text: I look forward to going here every week! The PT is great!, very professional too.. I feel relaxed, at times I fall asleep when I'm getting the ultrasound done, so comforting and relaxing... The atmosphere is very clean and music is soothing.. great staff too.

originalText.text: The office is very clean, staff is super friendly and helpful, and they offer a variety of services. This office does manual physical therapy, ultrasound therapy, taping, etc. They help with pain management as well as teach exercises that help your overall health! I would definitelt recommend!
